  "Description": {
    "English": "An unstable and highly-experimental piece of <span class=\"name name-technology\">freighter hyperdrive technology</span>. This extreme gravity device generates a <span class=\"name name-special\">wormhole</span> deep within the freighter's reactor core, inverting the entire vessel and transporting it across the universe.<br><br>Speak to the <span class=\"name name-stellar\">freighter's commander</span> to engage the drive. <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Warning</span>: destination is not controllable.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一件不稳定的、高度实验性的<span class=\"name name-technology\">货运飞船超光速推进器技术</span>。这个极端重力装置在货船反应堆核心深处产生一个<span class=\"name name-special\">虫洞</span>，将整艘船倒置，使其在宇宙中穿行。<br><br>与<span class=\"name name-stellar\">货船指挥官</span>对话，以启动该驱动器。<span class=\"name name-fuel\">警告</span>：目的地无法控制。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一種不穩定且高度實驗性質的<span class=\"name name-technology\">貨船超空間驅動器科技</span>。這種超重力裝置能夠在貨船的反應爐核心深處產生一個<span class=\"name name-special\">蟲洞</span>，顛倒整艘船艦，並在宇宙中瞬間移動。<br><br>和<span class=\"name name-stellar\">貨船指揮官</span>對話即可啟動此驅動器。<span class=\"name name-fuel\">警告</span>：無法控制目的地。"
  },
